description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 72, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 216, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60723-11610-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [216 Votes, Top 5% Score]
